===Etymology===
{{etyl|ang}} {{term|hleahtor}}, from {{proto|Germanic|hlahtroz}}.  Cognate with German {{term|Gelächter}}, Icelandic {{term|hlátur}}, Danish {{term|latter|lang=da}}.

